Water the flower         (Palace of Earth Spirits)

Objective
Make the large flower seed bloom on the center of the Palace and Protect it from attackers (spirits are attacking)



Outcome Everyone wins when the flower blooms fully

Defeat = Everyone is defeated or the flower wilts 

Methods
> Water it from watering cans (requires lots of water) 10 water buckets needed (Each Normal Room has 2 water source for 2 buckets (Explain logically what decoration can provide 2 water source each room that can be scooped by a bucket on the center))
> Get the water from the reservoir (needs large container or bucket)
> Get the water from the well (needs shovel and patience and strength check and bucket and rope)
> Using HQ Fertilizer to significantly boost the growth (Future bucket pour counts as 2 water)
> Transfering the seed to a more fertile ground (Located at Hidden)

Notes
> If someone begins to water the seed. The other party gets attacked immediately.
> Each party gets warped in a random normal room
> 

There is a well that is empty (requires a shovel)
And a lot of attempt to dig the water (One way to solve it) It contains 10 worths of water bucket



There is a map at the center. Where they can check and then use their intelligence check.
This will identify if they can accurately tell how long it will take to visit each location

Each room has a specific clue and items to loot


